      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in pristine condition. This MKIV retains its original 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, featuring the factory sequential twin-turbocharger setup and a perfectly synchronized Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis integrity is verified by matching VIN tags on all body panels, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of oxidation or fatigue. Performance is managed by the factory Torsen limited-slip differential and a double-wishbone suspension system maintained to strict factory tolerances. No aftermarket modifications; this is a pure, mechanically sound example of JDM engineering with a flawless interior and a drivetrain that exhibits peak compression and boost response.",
